comments: Hayward (CHA) cleanly deflects the ball away from Hield (SAC).
Hield (SAC) and Rozier (CHA) make incidental contact with one another as Rozier is passing the ball.
Fox (SAC) jumps A to B into Hayward's (CHA) body and affects his shot near the rim.
Barnes (SAC) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two legal steps after his gather.
Hayward (CHA) legally contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Rozier (CHA) and Hield (SAC) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Bridges (CHA) legally contests Hield's (SAC) driving shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) is moving alongside Hayward's (CHA) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Barnes (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Rozier (CHA) during rebounding.
Holmes (SAC) commits a take foul on Biyombo (CHA).
Biyombo (CHA) legally contests Fox's (SAC) driving shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) brushes Hayward's (CHA) side and contact is marginal.

Washington (CHA) attempts to inbound the ball to Rozier (CHA), and Rozier deflects it in the frontcourt before gaining possession of it in the backcourt. Since the pass was traveling to the backcourt, Rozier does not gain possession of the ball in the frontcourt, and inbounding the ball to the backcourt is legal in the last two minutes of play, there is no violation.
Barnes (SAC) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Hayward (CHA).
Bridges (CHA) legally contests Hield's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
